# Active Fitness App

The Fitness App project for the Mobile Application Development Coursework 2 of the BSc in Computer Science at Kingston University Uk, by ESoft Metro Campus Sri Lanka.

## Getting Started

1. Clone this repository's `main` branch.

```
git clone https://github.com/e184439/madcw2-fitness-app.git
```

2. Go to the project directory

```
cd madcw2-fitness-app
```

3. Compile the apk file using the following command.

```
flutter build apk --release
```

4. Then run the following command to install it to the device using ADB.

(Note: Replace `path/to/apk/file/madcw2-fitness-app.apk` to the real apk path of your computer.)

``` 
flutter install path/to/apk/file/madcw2-fitness-app.apk
```
